column4: Where is the SK office located in the barangay?
column6: Hi Vynce, SK office is located at Km. 6 San Francisco St. Brgy. Buhangin Proper, Davao City. You can ask me for details or other interests anytime.

column4: Are SK projects only for youth, or can the whole community benefit?
column6: Hi Vynce, PPAs are implemented and only intended for the youth. Additionally, we are also implementing PPAs that the whole Brgy Buhangin community can benefit from and enjoy. If that helps, tell me which one you want more details about.

column4: What types of programs does the SK Council usually implement?
column6: Hi Vynce, SK Council usually implements programs aligned with the 10 centers of youth participation: Social Inclusion, Health, Agriculture, Active Citizenship, Peace Building and Security, Education, Environment, Economic Empowerment, Global Mobility and Governance
